TITLE: Episode 42 - Whoever Wins... We Live
DESCRIPTION: In case you haven't heard, there was a presidential election yesterday. They say it was the MOST IMPORTANT ELECTION OF OUR LIFETIME! Instead of freaking out, let's take a step back and check our perspective.
